<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
At Bobo Analytics, we value the privacy and protection of user information.
This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, stored,
and protected when users visit our website or interact with our analytics
platform and services.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
We may collect personal information including name, email address,
business details, and communication data when users submit forms,
request demos, or contact us. Technical information such as IP address,
browser type, device information, and usage behavior may also be
automatically collected to improve platform performance and security.
</p>

<p>
This data helps us understand user behavior, optimize services,
and deliver better analytics experiences tailored to business needs.
We only collect information necessary for legitimate business purposes.
</p>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>

<p>
Collected data is used to respond to inquiries, provide analytics
services, improve website functionality, maintain security,
and communicate product updates. We may analyze aggregated data
to enhance platform intelligence and improve decision-making tools.
</p>

<p>
We do not sell personal information to third parties.
Information is processed responsibly and only shared with trusted
service providers when required for hosting, communication,
or technical operations.
</p>

<h2>Data Protection</h2>

<p>
We implement modern security practices including encrypted connections,
secure hosting infrastructure, and access controls to protect user data.
While no online system is completely secure, we continuously work to
maintain industry-standard safeguards.
</p>

<h2>User Rights</h2>

<p>
Users may request access, correction, or deletion of personal data
by contacting us. We respect privacy rights and respond to
reasonable requests in accordance with applicable regulations.
</p>

<h2>Policy Updates</h2>

<p>
This policy may be updated periodically to reflect service improvements
or regulatory changes. Continued use of the website indicates acceptance
of updated policies.
</p>

<p>
For privacy concerns, contact: support@boboanalytics.com
</p>

